<font face="Serif" size="18">こいつは</font>

351
00:14:18,495 --> 00:14:22,231
<font face="Serif" size="18">ミブロになろうとしたんだ。➡</font>

352
00:14:22,231 --> 00:14:24,231
<font face="Serif" size="18">それを…。</font>

353
00:14:24,231 --> 00:14:27,000
<font face="Serif" size="18">原田さん…。</font>

354
00:14:37,495 --> 00:14:40,825
<font face="Serif" size="18">私にだけ話とは？新見さん。</font>

355
00:14:44,330 --> 00:14:46,495
<font face="Serif" size="18">芹沢に幕を引かせる。</font>

356
00:14:46,495 --> 00:14:49,825
<font face="Serif" size="18">俺達は幕を下ろす。</font>

357
00:14:49,825 --> 00:14:51,825
<font face="Serif" size="18">まるで お二人とも➡</font>

358
00:14:51,825 --> 00:14:51,825
<font face="Serif" size="18">いなくなってしまうかのような</font>

359
00:14:51,825 --> 00:14:56,132
<font face="Serif" size="18">物言いですね。</font>

360
00:14:56,132 --> 00:14:58,132
<font face="Serif" size="18">失礼…。</font>

361
00:14:58,132 --> 00:14:58,132
<font face="Serif" size="18">新見さん あなたと芹沢さんは</font>

362
00:14:58,132 --> 00:15:01,330
<font face="Serif" size="18">つまり➡</font>

363
00:15:01,330 --> 00:15:03,825
<font face="Serif" size="18">どのような ご関係なのですか？</font>

364
00:15:03,825 --> 00:15:07,000
<font face="Serif" size="18">家が隣だった。</font>

365
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:07,000
<font face="Serif" size="18">(山南)それだけ？</font>

366
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:09,957
<font face="Serif" size="18">それだけだ。</font>

367
00:15:13,330 --> 00:15:17,000
<font face="Serif" size="18">山南 君にこれを。</font>

368
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:19,033
<font face="Serif" size="18">法度だ。</font>

369
00:15:19,033 --> 00:15:21,264
<font face="Serif" size="18">法度？</font>

370
00:15:21,264 --> 00:15:21,264
<font face="Serif" size="18">(新見)</font>

371
00:15:21,264 --> 00:15:21,264
<font face="Serif" size="18">これから隊士は</font>

372
00:15:21,264 --> 00:15:24,099
<font face="Serif" size="18">まだまだ増えるだろう。➡</font>

373
00:15:24,099 --> 00:15:24,099
<font face="Serif" size="18">新しく人が入れば</font>

374
00:15:24,099 --> 00:15:28,000
<font face="Serif" size="18">組織は乱れる。➡</font>

375
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:28,000
<font face="Serif" size="18">明確な決まりがない</font>

376
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:31,264
<font face="Serif" size="18">有象無象の集団では➡</font>

377
00:15:31,264 --> 00:15:34,495
<font face="Serif" size="18">京の街の魑魅魍魎とは戦えまい。➡</font>

378
00:15:34,495 --> 00:15:34,495
<font face="Serif" size="18">思いつくまま列挙したが</font>

379
00:15:34,495 --> 00:15:39,759
<font face="Serif" size="18">あくまで覚え書きであり 草案だ。</font>

380
00:15:39,759 --> 00:15:43,330
<font face="Serif" size="18">山南 君に完成させてほしい。</font>

381
00:15:43,330 --> 00:15:45,165
<font face="Serif" size="18">あ…。</font>

382
00:15:48,396 --> 00:15:50,396
<font face="Serif" size="18">《新見さん…》</font>

383
00:15:52,396 --> 00:15:54,891
<font face="Serif" size="18">《芹沢とは家が隣…➡</font>

384
00:15:54,891 --> 00:15:58,198
<font face="Serif" size="18">本当にそれだけの間柄だった》</font>

385
00:15:58,198 --> 00:15:58,198
<font face="Serif" size="18">回想 </font>

386
00:15:58,198 --> 00:15:58,198
<font face="Serif" size="18">(新見の声)</font>

387
00:15:58,198 --> 00:16:00,264
<font face="Serif" size="18">向こうは武士の四男坊。➡</font>

388
00:16:00,264 --> 00:16:00,264
<font face="Serif" size="18">俺は しがない</font>

389
00:16:00,264 --> 00:16:03,000
<font face="Serif" size="18">足軽の子だったが…➡</font>

390
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:03,000
<font face="Serif" size="18">あいつには 身分の差など</font>

391
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:07,561
<font face="Serif" size="18">何ら関係なかった。</font>

392
00:16:07,561 --> 00:16:07,561
<font face="Serif" size="18">(継次)伊織ぃ〜！</font>

393
00:16:07,561 --> 00:16:10,099
<font face="Serif" size="18">(伊織)継次…➡</font>

394
00:16:10,099 --> 00:16:12,099
<font face="Serif" size="18">どうしたんだ その顔。</font>

395
00:16:12,099 --> 00:16:14,099
<font face="Serif" size="18">親父にやられたんだ！</font>

396
00:16:14,099 --> 00:16:14,099
<font face="Serif" size="18">大事にしてたツボを</font>

397
00:16:14,099 --> 00:16:16,165
<font face="Serif" size="18">割っただけで！</font>

398
00:16:16,165 --> 00:16:18,165
<font face="Serif" size="18">２人で とっちめてやろうぜ！</font>

399
00:16:18,165 --> 00:16:18,165
<font face="Serif" size="18">とっちめるって</font>

400
00:16:18,165 --> 00:16:22,198
<font face="Serif" size="18">あの大男の親父さんを？</font>

401
00:16:22,198 --> 00:16:22,198
<font face="Serif" size="18">うっ…３人の兄共は</font>

402
00:16:22,198 --> 00:16:25,132
<font face="Serif" size="18">やっただろうが！</font>

403
00:16:25,132 --> 00:16:27,594
<font face="Serif" size="18">そのあと ボコボコにされただろ！</font>

404
00:16:27,594 --> 00:16:29,429
<font face="Serif" size="18">今度は殺されるぞ！</font>

405
00:16:29,429 --> 00:16:31,000
<font face="Serif" size="18">うぇ…！➡</font>

406
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:33,726
<font face="Serif" size="18">あ〜…やっぱ無理かぁ。</font>

407
00:16:35,726 --> 00:16:35,726
<font face="Serif" size="18">(伊織)奇襲だ…。</font>

408
00:16:35,726 --> 00:16:38,000
<font face="Serif" size="18">あ…奇襲!?</font>

409
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:38,000
<font face="Serif" size="18">二段落とし穴。</font>

410
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:40,693
<font face="Serif" size="18">(継次)二段!?</font>

411
00:16:44,330 --> 00:16:46,561
<font face="Serif" size="18">そろそろ来るはず…。</font>

412
00:16:48,561 --> 00:16:56,627
<font face="Serif" size="18">(足音)</font>

413
00:16:56,627 --> 00:16:56,627
<font face="Serif" size="18">落ちた〜！</font>

414
00:16:56,627 --> 00:16:58,825
<font face="Serif" size="18">(伊織)かかった！</font>

415
00:16:58,825 --> 00:16:58,825
<font face="Serif" size="18">(又衛門)ぐぐっ…ぬうぅ…。</font>

416
00:16:58,825 --> 00:17:01,561
<font face="Serif" size="18">(伊織)二段目も落ちたぞ！</font>

417
00:17:01,561 --> 00:17:01,561
<font face="Serif" size="18">行くぞ〜！</font>

418
00:17:01,561 --> 00:17:05,891
<font face="Serif" size="18">籠をかぶれ！面が割れるぞ！</font>

419
00:17:05,891 --> 00:17:05,891
<font face="Serif" size="18">(継次)たぁ〜 やっちまえ！</font>

420
00:17:05,891 --> 00:17:08,858
<font face="Serif" size="18">(又衛門)なに奴じゃ!?➡</font>

421
00:17:08,858 --> 00:17:08,858
<font face="Serif" size="18">継次だな！</font>

422
00:17:08,858 --> 00:17:11,759
<font face="Serif" size="18">ひいぃ！バレてる！</font>

423
00:17:11,759 --> 00:17:14,000
<font face="Serif" size="18">逃げろ！</font>

424
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:16,495
<font face="Serif" size="18">(又衛門)許さんぞ〜!!</font>

425
00:17:16,495 --> 00:17:18,891
<font face="Serif" size="18">(２人)はぁ…はぁ…。</font>

426
00:17:18,891 --> 00:17:18,891
<font face="Serif" size="18">はは！やった！</font>

427
00:17:18,891 --> 00:17:22,066
<font face="Serif" size="18">ざま〜みろ！</font>

428
00:17:22,066 --> 00:17:24,198
<font face="Serif" size="18">面白かったな！</font>

429
00:17:24,198 --> 00:17:26,759
<font face="Serif" size="18">逆襲には備えなくちゃな。</font>

430
00:17:26,759 --> 00:17:26,759
<font face="Serif" size="18">俺の力と</font>

431
00:17:26,759 --> 00:17:30,264
<font face="Serif" size="18">お前の頭があれば無敵だ！</font>

432
00:17:30,264 --> 00:17:32,858
<font face="Serif" size="18">次は 寄合所を襲おうぜ！</font>

433
00:17:32,858 --> 00:17:32,858
<font face="Serif" size="18">寄合所か。</font>

434
00:17:32,858 --> 00:17:36,528
<font face="Serif" size="18">あそこは凶暴な犬がいるぞ。</font>

435
00:17:36,528 --> 00:17:36,528
<font face="Serif" size="18">(継次)どうする!?</font>

436
00:17:36,528 --> 00:17:40,726
<font face="Serif" size="18">(伊織)そうだな まずは…。</font>

437
00:17:40,726 --> 00:17:43,561
<font face="Serif" size="18">現在 </font>

438
00:17:43,561 --> 00:17:45,726
<font face="Serif" size="18">ん？➡</font>

439
00:17:45,726 --> 00:17:45,726
<font face="Serif" size="18">新見 他の奴らはまだ来んのか？</font>

440
00:17:45,726 --> 00:17:51,066
<font face="Serif" size="18">酒宴はどうした？</font>

441
00:17:51,066 --> 00:17:51,066
<font face="Serif" size="18">酒宴はない。</font>

442
00:17:51,066 --> 00:17:54,660
<font face="Serif" size="18">来るのはお前１人だ。</font>

443
00:17:54,660 --> 00:17:54,660
<font face="Serif" size="18">あぁん？</font>

444
00:17:54,660 --> 00:17:57,627
<font face="Serif" size="18">こうして向かい合うのは➡</font>

445
00:17:57,627 --> 00:18:00,759
<font face="Serif" size="18">いつ以来かな…継次よ。</font>

446
00:18:00,759 --> 00:18:04,000
<font face="Serif" size="18">つっ…あははっ！</font>

447
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:04,000
<font face="Serif" size="18">何十億年ぶりに</font>

448
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:07,066
<font face="Serif" size="18">その名で呼ばれたわ➡</font>

449
00:18:07,066 --> 00:18:09,066
<font face="Serif" size="18">伊織よ。</font>

450
00:18:09,066 --> 00:18:09,066
<font face="Serif" size="18">大座敷を貸し切ってまで</font>

451
00:18:09,066 --> 00:18:12,363
<font face="Serif" size="18">わざわざ呼び出すとは➡</font>

452
00:18:12,363 --> 00:18:15,660
<font face="Serif" size="18">ずいぶん手が込んでるのう。</font>

453
00:18:15,660 --> 00:18:17,924
<font face="Serif" size="18">もう 終いにしよう。</font>

454
00:18:17,924 --> 00:18:20,495
<font face="Serif" size="18">あ？</font>

455
00:18:20,495 --> 00:18:20,495
<font face="Serif" size="18">商屋や金持ちの被害の記録と</font>

456
00:18:20,495 --> 00:18:25,000
<font face="Serif" size="18">隊内の粛清。➡</font>

457
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:25,000
<font face="Serif" size="18">５人の検死結果。</font>

458
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:29,726
<font face="Serif" size="18">そして行方不明者６名の行方…➡</font>

459
00:18:29,726 --> 00:18:29,726
<font face="Serif" size="18">すべてお前が絡んでいると</font>

460
00:18:29,726 --> 00:18:33,231
<font face="Serif" size="18">見ている。➡</font>

461
00:18:33,231 --> 00:18:36,000
<font face="Serif" size="18">伝えるべきことも伝えた➡</font>

462
00:18:36,000 --> 00:18:38,066
<font face="Serif" size="18">もうミブロは大丈夫だ。</font>

463
00:18:40,561 --> 00:18:40,561
<font face="Serif" size="18">おいおい</font>

464
00:18:40,561 --> 00:18:44,594
<font face="Serif" size="18">宴席に刀を持ち込むとは➡</font>

465
00:18:44,594 --> 00:18:47,231
<font face="Serif" size="18">無作法がすぎるではないか。</font>

466
00:18:49,528 --> 00:18:51,660
<font face="Serif" size="18">けじめを。</font>

467
00:18:51,660 --> 00:18:54,660
<font face="Serif" size="18">俺達の役目は終わった。</font>

468
00:18:54,660 --> 00:18:57,924
<font face="Serif" size="18">お前は どうする？</font>

469
00:18:57,924 --> 00:19:00,198
<font face="Serif" size="18">すぐに あとを追う。</font>

470
00:19:04,660 --> 00:19:07,330
<font face="Serif" size="18">(新見)魂は螺旋を描く。</font>

471
00:19:07,330 --> 00:19:07,330
<font face="Serif" size="18">人は死ねば</font>

472
00:19:07,330 --> 00:19:10,429
<font face="Serif" size="18">また赤子として生まれる。</font>

473
00:19:10,429 --> 00:19:10,429
<font face="Serif" size="18">その繰り返しだ。</font>

474
00:19:10,429 --> 00:19:13,495
<font face="Serif" size="18">出来うるならば➡</font>

475
00:19:13,495 --> 00:19:13,495
<font face="Serif" size="18">永遠に同じ時の中を</font>

476
00:19:13,495 --> 00:19:16,792
<font face="Serif" size="18">繰り返したいものだ。</font>

477
00:19:16,792 --> 00:19:19,363
<font face="Serif" size="18">なんだ それは？</font>

478
00:19:19,363 --> 00:19:21,363
<font face="Serif" size="18">死生観。</font>

479
00:19:21,363 --> 00:19:24,561
<font face="Serif" size="18">くだらん。人生は一度きりよ。</font>

480
00:19:24,561 --> 00:19:24,561
<font face="Serif" size="18">だから やりたいように</font>

481
00:19:24,561 --> 00:19:27,429
<font face="Serif" size="18">やってきたのだ。➡</font>

482
00:19:27,429 --> 00:19:31,000
<font face="Serif" size="18">終わらせる か…。➡</font>

483
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:35,660
<font face="Serif" size="18">いいだろう。ただし…➡</font>

484
00:19:35,660 --> 00:19:38,429
<font face="Serif" size="18">伊織 貴様だけだ。➡</font>

485
00:19:38,429 --> 00:19:38,429
<font face="Serif" size="18">情に訴えれば</font>

486
00:19:38,429 --> 00:19:41,858
<font face="Serif" size="18">人が動くと思ったか。➡</font>

487
00:19:41,858 --> 00:19:41,858
<font face="Serif" size="18">だからお前は甘い。</font>

488
00:19:41,858 --> 00:19:46,297
<font face="Serif" size="18">貴様の弱点だ。</font>

489
00:19:46,297 --> 00:19:46,297
<font face="Serif" size="18">伊織 お前は</font>

490
00:19:46,297 --> 00:19:49,693
<font face="Serif" size="18">ここで切腹をするのだ。</font>

491
00:19:49,693 --> 00:19:52,396
<font face="Serif" size="18">いま殺してそう見せかけるのは➡</font>

492
00:19:52,396 --> 00:19:55,165
<font face="Serif" size="18">造作もないことよ。</font>

493
00:19:55,165 --> 00:19:57,165
<font face="Serif" size="18">ふっ…。</font>

494
00:19:57,165 --> 00:19:59,330
<font face="Serif" size="18">なにを笑っている？</font>

495
00:19:59,330 --> 00:20:02,462
<font face="Serif" size="18">あの時代はよかった。➡</font>

496
00:20:02,462 --> 00:20:06,924
<font face="Serif" size="18">物事はわかりやすく 単純だった。</font>

497
00:20:06,924 --> 00:20:09,660
<font face="Serif" size="18">だが少しずつ大人になり➡</font>

498
00:20:09,660 --> 00:20:09,660
<font face="Serif" size="18">場所が変わり人が変わり</font>

499
00:20:09,660 --> 00:20:13,660
<font face="Serif" size="18">時代が変わった。➡</font>

500
00:20:13,660 --> 00:20:16,000
<font face="Serif" size="18">複雑になったな。</font>

501
00:20:16,000 --> 00:20:16,000
<font face="Serif" size="18">さあ殺れよ。</font>

502
00:20:16,000 --> 00:20:19,891
<font face="Serif" size="18">自害に見せかけるんだろう？➡</font>

503
00:20:19,891 --> 00:20:22,495
<font face="Serif" size="18">うちの監察達は優秀だ。➡</font>

504
00:20:22,495 --> 00:20:25,660
<font face="Serif" size="18">必ず捏造を見破るだろう。</font>

505
00:20:25,660 --> 00:20:27,693
<font face="Serif" size="18">局長が殺られたとあっては➡</font>

506
00:20:27,693 --> 00:20:30,000
<font face="Serif" size="18">近藤達も捨ておけない。</font>

507
00:20:30,000 --> 00:20:32,429
<font face="Serif" size="18">奴らはお前を殺しに来るだろう。</font>

508
00:20:32,429 --> 00:20:35,066
<font face="Serif" size="18">伊織！貴様ぁ！</font>

509
00:20:35,066 --> 00:20:38,891
<font face="Serif" size="18">そうなったら 面白いじゃないか。</font>

510
00:20:38,891 --> 00:20:40,891
<font face="Serif" size="18">なに？</font>

511
00:20:40,891 --> 00:20:43,066
<font face="Serif" size="18">どうせなら 芹沢 鴨は➡</font>

512
00:20:43,066 --> 00:20:45,330
<font face="Serif" size="18">戦って死にたいだろう。</font>

513
00:20:45,330 --> 00:20:45,330
<font face="Serif" size="18">鉄砲で その他大勢として</font>

514
00:20:45,330 --> 00:20:49,066
<font face="Serif" size="18">死ぬなんて ごめんだろう。➡</font>

515
00:20:49,066 --> 00:20:49,066
<font face="Serif" size="18">ましてや 病に倒れ</font>

516
00:20:49,066 --> 00:20:53,000
<font face="Serif" size="18">老いさらばえるなんて➡</font>

517
00:20:53,000 --> 00:20:55,165
<font face="Serif" size="18">もってのほか。</font>

518
00:20:55,165 --> 00:20:57,924
<font face="Serif" size="18">俺達は好きだったじゃないか➡</font>

519
00:20:57,924 --> 00:21:01,198
<font face="Serif" size="18">一杯食わせてやるのが。</font>

520
00:21:08,792 --> 00:21:08,792
<font face="Serif" size="18">聞こう。</font>

521
00:21:08,792 --> 00:21:12,825
<font face="Serif" size="18">(新見)そうだな まずは…。</font>

522
00:21:12,825 --> 00:21:32,000
<font face="Serif" size="18">♬〜</font>

523
00:21:35,396 --> 00:21:38,198
